cap per instrument-sim voice. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-025 | Implement R11 Call-Response Gating: follower phrase intent complements leader's realized performance. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-026 | Compose SectionEnvelope with phrase arcs multiplicatively so section-level tempo elasticity modulates phrase-level shaping. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-027 | Implement tempo-dependent swing curve per Friberg/Sundström (3.5:1 at slow tempi down toward 1:1 at fast), with short-note near-constant ~100 ms. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-028 | Add arc-shape variety so not every phrase uses a symmetric parabola: per-phrase random selection from parabolic/cosine/asymmetric-Bezier/flat/inverted with peak-position variance. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-029 | Implement restraint parameter enforced as global dampener across rules. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-030 | Implement R12 Sensor-to-Intent Aggregation Matrix: smoothed IIR + hysteresis → aggregate intentions (global_energy, global_restraint, global_brightness). | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-031 | Implement bounded reactive delta track in scheduler with per-parameter modulation caps. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-032 | Couple narrative engine to SectionEnvelope selection so dramatic arcs drive section choice. | SHOULD | T2 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-033 | Expose aggregate-intention telemetry (global_energy/restraint/brightness) in operator diagnostics, never raw one-to-one mappings. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-034 | Build the metric battery: IOI CoV, velocity σ, DNVR/DNODR, pitch-class entropy H1, Grooving Similarity (GS), tempo autocorrelation ρ₁, LZ76 compression ratio, novelty peaks per phrase, silence-at-phrase-boundaries. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-035 | Build anti-pattern tests: quantization ghosting, dynamic compression, motif ossification, random-as-expression (Ljung-Box), symmetric-arc uncanny, dead-silence